snippet.title: Dangling sign a High St hazard
snippet.content: THIS sign has seen better days. The Leader snapped these pictures of a dangling sign outside an abandoned shop front in High St, Preston today. Pedestrians should steer clear of the sign, which hangs on a busy stretch of High St on the corner of Bell St, near a bus stop and several cafes. Darebin Council has been tipped off to the potential hazard.
